author: Joey Hadden
title: Healthcare professionals around the world are sharing photos of their exhausted faces, sometimes bruised from masks, after harrowing shifts treating coronavirus patients. They all have the same message: Stay home.
description: Doctors and nurses all around the world are fighting on the frontlines of COVID-19 as the coronavirus continues to spread globally. They are taking photos of their faces after long, exhausting shifts of testing and treating potential COVID-19 patients, and so…
